    <meta name="description" content="ECHOPILLS is an ISO 9001:2015 certified B2B supplier of housekeeping, hygiene, FMCG, chemical, dispensers, and corporate gifting products. Procure commercial cleaning tools, TASKI chemicals, garbage bags, dispensers, and more. Serving Bengaluru and pan-India.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="ECHOPILLS, housekeeping products, hygiene products, corporate gifting, FMCG, TASKI chemicals, Diversey, vacuum cleaner, floor scrubber, wipers, brooms, dispensers, aerosol dispenser, urinal screen, room freshener, garbage bag, duster, scraper, Bengaluru, ISO 9001:2015">
